						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">dougeff wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">It kinda looks like she's not wearing anything below the waist but thong underwear</div><br /><br />She has boots. Those are below the waist. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">dougeff wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">and after she pulls the sword out, she's not so much walking, but shimmying and shaking her butt. Just saying'.</div><br /><br />That's kind of the idea. If her sword is sheathed, she can walk but would attack slower. If she draws, she can attack quicker but her mobility is lowered. It's not so much of a walk as a scoot, and slightly over exaggerated for cartoon purposes. I did a few different tries on that one, and in reality, she wouldn't have to kneel down like that to move in that way, but with her short little cartoon legs she kind of does, plus the up and down really added a lot of movement to the character so I left it in.</div>

